Package ide.backend.blocks.variablesAndTypes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GetVarBlock
    This Block is used to use the content of a variable.
    SetBlock  
    SetReturnBlock
    This block is used to fetch the returnValues from the stack for these variable and set the variables in the function where another function was called equal to these values.
    ValueBlock
    A block which creates a new valueVariable containing the value the user provided via userinput in the IDE.
    VariableBlock
    Creates a new variable of a given type [type] and name [name] onto the current stackframe
